     count. Used instead of `min-content` so grid-template-columns animates
     between two lengths: WebKit/iOS collapses a track that transitions
     between a length and an intrinsic keyword (min-content), where Chrome and
     Firefox snap it to the final size instead. */
  --active-filters-width: calc(
    var(--active-filters-list-length) * 168px +
    (var(--active-filters-list-length) - 1) * 8px
  );
  grid-template-columns: 0px 0px 0px 0px;
